cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.NA 

This paper is about image denoising, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses optimization and weighting of filters, which are topics in machine learning (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT). The authors also mention the use of mean-squared-error (MSE) as a metric, which is commonly used in machine learning and statistics (cs.LG). Finally, the paper proposes a fast algorithm for the weighted filtering, which could fall under numerical analysis (cs.NA).
